description:
--> Smart, stimulating and interactive vehicle - matching and memory games for children 
--> Playful, lively animations, interactive scenes! 
--> Games combine focus, concentration and fine motor skills with moving shapes and puzzles 
 
Young kids love vehicles and things that fly and parents love smart games.  From planes and trucks to motorcycles and rocket ships, the My Vehicle Universe app brings the excitement and passion kids have for transportation into a fun educational game.  Young children can learn to recognize dozens of vehicles from construction trucks and buses to bulldozers and taxi cabs. We provide a full universe of vehicles - 8 unique categories - and integrate memory games and shapes and sizes into an action-packed app.  
 
Features:
--> 8 different categories: transport, emergency, boats, sports, planes, cars, space, construction.
--> Play with vehicles and match their drivers, improve fine motor skills along with memory, focus and concentration.
--> 17 pages of beautiful HD illustrations combined with rich interactive modes.
--> Easy to use - especially designed for children.
